{"tid":258200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天眼影晒】買外賣1分鐘    內地女唔見iPhone7 Plus","createTime":"2017-05-26T01:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T08:37:23.000Z","uid":48093,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe2eb75a4f1aab27362e90f7808ef1e94a67ce18","tid":258200,"uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T01:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170525/large/1495723702_4526.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170525%2Flarge%2F1495723702_4526.jpg&h=04d39587&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【09:20更新】楊小姐稱事發時間應為前日中午12時黑雨期間。<br />\n<br />\n內地女買外賣畀錢1分鐘，枱上iPhone7 Plus被偷走！由內地來港公幹的楊小姐，前日中午與友人到沙田河畔花園一餐廳買外賣，她付款時將手機交給友人看管，詎料對方將手機放在收銀櫃前忘記取回。兩人於旁邊等候外賣期間，懵然不知手機仍在收銀枱面，剛巧一名短髮女子排隊埋單，拿起手機查看後，便順手拿走，全程僅約1分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n楊小姐其後拿著外賣離開，上車後才驚覺遺失手機，連忙折返餐廳查問，並報警求助。她昨日翻看閉路電視錄影，發現偷手機女子的容貌，惟警方表示案件較難搜證，安慰叫她「睇開啲」。<br />\n<br />\n楊小姐事後向《蘋果》表示，被偷走的手機為iPhone7 Plus，5日前在香港購買，雖然沒有有儲存重要資料或相片，但亦感到難過。"},{"pid":"e300c0446928b34e5489753fe3e59fedbaac75fc","tid":258200,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T01:41:45.000Z","msg":"tb ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191c2ba3fd1bf782f2021c9f0f533f57924a8314","tid":258200,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T01:44:24.000Z","msg":"睇住佢偷都搜唔到證？"},{"pid":"416a9f0581dd210ea4e548d5392ce9f15a4f8d90","tid":258200,"uid":4975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T01:47:41.000Z","msg":"警察又唔做嘢了"},{"pid":"438de7cb83ee89a9c94e62e41cf4460d43ec2d2d","tid":258200,"uid":521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T01:48:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇住佢偷都搜唔到證？</blockquote><br />\n阿sir做野..."},{"pid":"7dcdf1c2904f7aa9f806d80ab93e8761792bbc55","tid":258200,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-